<h2 class="mt-20">Disable touch swiping <a href=""id="Disable-touch-swiping" class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
<p >
On touchscreen devices, carousels allow you to swipe left or right to switch between slides. By utilizing the <code>data-bs-touch </code> attribute, this can be turned off. Additionally, the example below lacks the <code>data-bs-ride</code> feature and does not autoplay.
</p>
